     "group": "Suspension of access to systems",
     "name": "overview",
     "prose": {
      "en": "Removing or suspending access to systems and their resources, ideally using an automatic mechanism, can prevent them from being accessed when there is no longer a legitimate business requirement for their use, such as when personnel change duties, leave an organisation or are detected undertaking malicious activities."
